    title: "Building Your Daily Wellness Protocol: A Complete Guide for Indian Lifestyles",
    category: "Wellness",
    excerpt: "A practical, evidence-based daily ritual integrating plant botanicals, lifestyle practices, and mindfulness tools designed specifically for the Indian urban professional.",
